{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843586398,"sessionID":"ses_2877b1772ffeiGgFV0JJ2qd1m4","part":{"id":"prt_d788625a7001beLWqEsxmfyxmj","messageID":"msg_d78861846001v58XC8Hpc3Vg48","sessionID":"ses_2877b1772ffeiGgFV0JJ2qd1m4","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_5e018cf777b14450b0e488c4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-1 (Draft)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Deletion Handlers\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleSandboxDelete() handler for DELETE by SessionID\n- [ ] **1.2** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleSandboxDeleteByName() handler for DELETE by name\n- [ ] **1.3** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` - Register DELETE routes: /v1/namespaces/{ns}/sandboxes/{sessionId}, /v1/namespaces/{ns}/sandboxes/name/{name}\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/delete_options.go` - DeleteOptions struct with GracePeriodSeconds, Force, LabelSelector fields\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Graceful Shutdown\n\n- [ ] **2.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_shutdown.go` - gracefulDeleter struct\n- [ ] **2.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_shutdown.go` - drainConnections() to stop routing new traffic\n- [ ] **2.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_shutdown.go` - waitForConnections() with timeout\n- [ ] **2.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_shutdown.go` - executePreDeleteHook() for lifecycle hooks\n- [ ] **2.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_shutdown.go` - sendSIGTERM() to container\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: TTL and Expiration\n\n- [ ] **3.1** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - Add TTL check logic\n- [ ] **3.2** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - Add idle timeout detection\n- [ ] **3.3** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - Add MaxLifetime enforcement\n- [ ] **3.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration.go` - isExpired() helper for TTL/Idle/MaxLifetime checks\n- [ ] **3.5** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go` - Add DefaultTTL, DefaultIdleTimeout, DefaultMaxLifetime constants\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Batch Operations\n\n- [ ] **4.1** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleDeleteAllSandboxes() for namespace-wide deletion\n- [ ] **4.2** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleDeleteByLabelSelector() for filtered deletion\n- [ ] **4.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/batch_delete.go` - deleteStaleSandboxes() for Unknown/Failed state cleanup\n- [ ] **4.4** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` - Register DELETE /v1/namespaces/{ns}/sandboxes with query params\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Lifecycle Events and Webhooks\n\n- [ ] **5.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_events.go` - emitDeletionEvent() using event recorder\n- [ ] **5.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_events.go` - sendDeletionWebhook() with retry logic\n- [ ] **5.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_events.go` - logDeletionAudit() for audit trail\n- [ ] **5.4** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` - Add WebhookConfig, AuditLogEntry types\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Resource Cleanup\n\n- [ ] **6.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup.go` - cleanupServices() to delete owned Services\n- [ ] **6.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup.go` - cleanupConfigMaps() to delete owned ConfigMaps\n- [ ] **6.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup.go` - cleanupPVCs() with ReclaimPolicy handling\n- [ ] **6.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup.go` - cleanupOrphanedResources() for external deletions\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Error Handling\n\n- [ ] **7.1** Update error types in `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` - Add ErrSandboxNotFound, ErrDeletionFailed, ErrStaleFinalizer\n- [ ] **7.2** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Map error types to HTTP status codes\n- [ ] **7.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/retry.go` - retryDeletion() with exponential backoff\n- [ ] **7.4** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - Add retry logic for failed deletions\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Integration with AR-005\n\n- [ ] **8.1** Integrate with sandbox_creator: Handle cleanup on creation failure (rollback)\n- [ ] **8.2** Integrate with store: Call DeleteSandbox(), GetSandbox() for deletion verification\n- [ ] **8.3** Integrate with k8s_client: Use dynamic client for deletion operations\n- [ ] **8.4** Ensure graceful shutdown integrates with existing informer watches\n\n---\n\n## Phase 9: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **9.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_delete_test.go` - TestHandleSandboxDelete_Success\n- [ ] **9.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_delete_test.go` - TestHandleSandboxDelete_NotFound\n- [ ] **9.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_delete_test.go` - TestHandleSandboxDelete_Force\n- [ ] **9.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_shutdown_test.go` - TestDrainConnections\n- [ ] **9.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_shutdown_test.go` - TestExecutePreDeleteHook\n- [ ] **9.6** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go` - TestTTLExpiration\n- [ ] **9.7** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go` - TestIdleTimeout\n- [ ] **9.8** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/batch_delete_test.go` - TestDeleteAllInNamespace\n- [ ] **9.9** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/batch_delete_test.go` - TestDeleteByLabelSelector\n- [ ] **9.10** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_events_test.go` - TestEmitDeletionEvent\n- [ ] **9.11** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup_test.go` - TestCleanupServices\n- [ ] **9.12** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration_test.go` - TestIsExpired_TTL\n- [ ] **9.13** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration_test.go` - TestIsExpired_IdleTimeout\n\n---\n\n## Phase 10: Integration Tests\n\n- [ ] **10.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/integration_delete_test.go` - E2E test for sandbox deletion\n- [ ] **10.2** Test graceful shutdown with active connections\n- [ ] **10.3** Test TTL expiration and cleanup\n- [ ] **10.4** Test batch deletion with 100+ sandboxes\n\n---\n\n## Phase 11: Verification\n\n- [ ] **11.1** Run `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - successful compilation\n- [ ] **11.2** Run `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - all unit tests pass\n- [ ] **11.3** Run `go test -race ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - no race conditions\n- [ ] **11.4** Run `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - no issues\n- [ ] **11.5** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - linter passes\n- [ ] **11.6** Verify test coverage > 40% with `go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| Phase 1 | AR-005 (Sandbox 创建处理器) |\n| Phase 2 | Phase 1 (handlers) |\n| Phase 3 | Phase 1 (handlers) |\n| Phase 4 | Phase 1-3 |\n| Phase 5 | Phase 1 (handlers) |\n| Phase 6 | AR-005 (k8s_client, informers) |\n| Phase 7 | Phase 1 (types) |\n| Phase 8 | AR-005 (sandbox_creator, store, k8s_client) |\n| Phase 9 | Phase 1-8 (implementation complete) |\n| Phase 10 | Phase 9 (unit tests) |\n| Phase 11 | All phases |\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design: `sandbox-orchestration/AR-006-sandbox-deletion-lifecycle/design.md`\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md`\n- Related AR: AR-005 (Sandbox 创建处理器)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-006/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-006/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-006/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775843586389,"end":1775843586395}}}}
